Made in Photoshop 7.
Uses selective color.
Don't claim as your own.
Add to memories if you like it. :D
Please comment!
Show me your results.
Friend the journal for any personal entries. But first, leave me a comment.
And enjoy! ;)

Open up your image. I used this one of Hayden Panettiere.
Layer>New adjustment layer>Selective color
Reds: - 100, 0, +50, -30
Cyans: +59, -49, +100, 0

Layer>New adjustment layer>Selective color
Reds: -21, +13, - 20, 0

And you're done. Now, was that easy? I think so. :D
